@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_inmppc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (0.32 * 0.16)
    v0 = (wp.exp((v2 + 0.83 / tmp + 0.80)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.03 + v0 + 0.56)))
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(v1 + 0.61)) * ((v2 + 0.45 - tmp + 0.78) + wp.exp(v2 + 0.81)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.66))
    tmp = v2
    v0 = wp.sin(0.83)
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
